response.original_title: Witchcraft: The Magick Rituals of the Coven
response.overview: The History and Craft of Modern Day Witches. Karen Frandsen from Eerie Investigations interviews Jeanette Ellis, lecturer on traditional British Witchcraft, member of PEBL, and author of "Forbidden Rites." Jeanette reveals the truth behind many aspects of Witchcraft.
